  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nThe config file is completely erased if the JSON is incorrectly formatted.\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. Broke your config file - for example remove a required comma.\r\n2. Run the node\r\n3. You should get:\r\n```\r\n2022-09-21 17:39:23.7995|Failure System.Configuration.ConfigurationErrorsException: Config is not correctly formed JSon. See inner exception for details.\r\n ---> Newtonsoft.Json.JsonReaderException: Error reading JToken from JsonReader. Path '', line 0, position 0.\r\n   at Newtonsoft.Json.Linq.JToken.ReadFrom(JsonReader reader, JsonLoadSettings settings)\r\n   at Newtonsoft.Json.Linq.JToken.Parse(String json, JsonLoadSettings settings)\r\n   at Nethermind.Config.JsonConfigSource.ApplyJsonConfig(String jsonContent) in /root/src/nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Config/JsonConfigSource.cs:line 37\r\n   --- End of inner exception stack trace ---\r\n   at Nethermind.Config.JsonConfigSource.ApplyJsonConfig(String jsonContent) in /root/src/nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Config/JsonConfigSource.cs:line 45\r\n   at Nethermind.Config.JsonConfigSource.LoadJsonConfig(String configFilePath) in /root/src/nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Config/JsonConfigSource.cs:line 51\r\n   at Nethermind.Config.JsonConfigSource..ctor(String configFilePath) in /root/src/nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Config/JsonConfigSource.cs:line 30\r\n   at Nethermind.Runner.Program.BuildConfigProvider(CommandLineApplication app, CommandOption loggerConfigSource, CommandOption logLevelOverride, CommandOption configsDirectory, CommandOption configFile) in /root/src/nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Runner/Program.cs:line 401\r\n   at Nethermind.Runner.Program.<>c__DisplayClass10_0.<<Run>b__2>d.MoveNext() in /root/src/nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Runner/Program.cs:line 138\r\n```\r\n4. Check if your config file is empty now.",
